data.description: Wonderful custom home on 5.74 sub dividable acres in Golden Valley. Home is amazing offering a private long driveway to your secluded property with a nice 3 bedroom home with attached sunroom. Home offers many great features including a pellet stove on thermostat to keep you nice and warm, large master bath, walk in closet and attached 2 car garage. HUGE detached RV garage that allows you to park 2 RVs inside and drive them through the garage and an attached large workshop/garage with its own bathroom. Property can be subdivided into as small as 1 acre lots. Tons of room for toys, RVs, horses and animals. Seller has taken great care of the property and added many upgrades. There is an RV dump, 220V in RV garage, 2 pressure tanks, reverse osmosis, new Pure water system, new hot water tank, central vac, chicken coop, and dog pen with dog house, skylights with shades, and wonderful fruit trees. You won't want to miss this opportunity!
